<p>In a statement published on the university's news website on Wednesday, the University of Connecticut (UConn) Health Center
said the investigation has led them to inform 11 scientific journals that had published studies conducted by Dr Dipak K. Das, a
professor in the unversity's Department of Surgery and director of its Cardiovascular Research Center.</p>
<p>According to a report from the Associated Press (AP), Dr Nir Barzilai, whose team conducts resveratrol research at the Albert
Einstein College of Medicine in New York, says Das is not a major player in the field.</p>
